{
  "stem": "3360.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the last four years, we lived somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- [COUGHING] Excuse me-- 1934 or '35, or late '34, until '39, when we left Hamburg for good.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the first school I went to was the Kielort Allee, which I spelled earlier, where I had my four happy years, and was-- there was no such thing as anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There wasn't anything like, you're a Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't play with you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That came later.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was totally, complete acceptance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, this Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Rosenberg-- and that's not a Jewish Rosenberg, that's a German Rosenberg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember him telling my mother at a conference-- and I guess he didn't say it quietly enough.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, you know, I like having Jewish kids in my class.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They catch on so quickly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I remember him saying that, and he didn't like dumb students.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's one thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He went around with his-- when somebody didn't pay attention, he went and-- that was before we had all the problems.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We can't touch a child, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nowadays, he wouldn't be able do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He had a ruler in his hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He, he went across the knuckles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I was one of his favorites, so I never experienced that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we, we must have had a very good, must have gotten or received a very good foundation there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "If you didn't learn your pieces-- your spelling, your arithmetic, if you didn't write your sentences correctly, your grammar, you did not move on to the next grade.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was just-- you know, you had to do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was, there was hours of homework after we got home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was taken seriously, and it was a must.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we, we would take these field trips, very early on already.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
